# Google OAuth2 Credentials
# Get these from https://console.cloud.google.com/
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id_here
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_google_client_secret_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Create a new project or select existing project
# 3. Enable Gmail API in APIs & Services
# 4. Create OAuth 2.0 credentials in Credentials section
# 5. Add http://localhost:8000/api/oauth-callback to authorized redirect URIs
# 6. Copy the client ID and secret to this file
# 7. Rename this file to .env